we was gonna have to hurry,

1212
01:32:11,124 --> 01:32:14,624
and she wasn't sure
she could do it.

1213
01:32:17,628 --> 01:32:20,630
Willa Mae... your mama...

1214
01:32:20,631 --> 01:32:22,132
took my hand.

1215
01:32:23,633 --> 01:32:25,600
Told me she hurt bad

1216
01:32:25,635 --> 01:32:28,637
