her baby to die.

1217
01:32:28,672 --> 01:32:32,640
She asked me if I thought
the good Lord was punishing her

1218
01:32:32,641 --> 01:32:35,642
for how the baby come to be.

1219
01:32:36,142 --> 01:32:39,645
