all the little babies.

1223
01:32:48,153 --> 01:32:52,656
Then she say,
"Tiara, go get Raymond. "

1224
01:32:54,658 --> 01:32:56,158
She wanted to see you

1225
01:32:56,659 --> 01:33:00,162
